    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  21 years of age or older, and no greater than 65 years of age

          -  Medically stable

          -  Smoke at least 15 filtered cigarettes daily

          -  Motivated to quit smoking

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Medically unstable

          -  Currently psychiatrically unstable (schizophrenia, unstable psychosis, untreated major
             depression, active substance abuse within the past 6 months)

          -  Pregnant
      </textblock>
